  "title": "IT Sourcing Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Lead end-to-end IT sourcing and procurement for banking initiatives</p></li><li><p>Drive sourcing for IT transformation projects and strategic programs</p></li><li><p>Manage RFP/RFQ/RFI processes and vendor evaluations</p></li><li><p>Negotiate contracts, licensing, SLAs, and renewals</p></li><li><p>Deliver cost savings through spend analysis and vendor optimization</p></li><li><p>Ensure procurement governance, compliance, and audit readiness</p></li><li><p>Manage vendor performance and stakeholder relationships</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>8–12 years of IT procurement / sourcing experience</p></li><li><p>Mandatory experience in Banking or Financial Services</p></li><li><p>Strong exposure to software, cloud, infrastructure, and IT services</p></li><li><p>Proven contract negotiation and vendor management expertise</p></li><li><p>Familiarity with APAC regulatory and compliance requirements</p></li><li><p>Procurement certifications (CIPS preferred)<br /><br />EA Number: 11C4879 </p></li></ul>",
